        <p class="text-xl italic text-gray-700">
          "Santorini's beauty lies not just in its famous blue domes, but in the way light plays across its whitewashed walls and the drama of its volcanic landscape."
        </p>
      </blockquote>

      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <div class="bg-brand-blue/5 rounded-xl p-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-4">Save Inspiration for Later</h2>
